<item>
            <title>[HBASE-10757] Change HTable class doc so it sends people to HCM getting instances</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10757</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The HTable class doc does not reflect the new regime where you are meant to go via cluster connection to get an instance.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Getting an HTable otherwise also makes for some strange issues:  See &quot;Occasional GSSException that brings down region server&quot; on mailing list.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
